          <p class='first-para'>
            I am not giving way. As my noble friend said on Second Reading, I shall give way when it suits. I hope that he will look at <span class="italic">Hansard</span> carefully and see whether it was possible to infer the fact that the Government would want such a power to deal with society and, more particularly, public sector institutions, and in this case the fire services, irrespective of other circumstances and in particular the agreement of the parties. That is all that I ask.
          </p>
